data.title: MB21 Transcript
data.meta_description:
MB21_transcript - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. 1) The author, Victoria Mountbatten, was born in 1863 at Windsor Castle. She had many godparents including Queen Marie Amelie of France. 

2) During her early childhood, Victoria lived with her parents and grandparents in Darmstadt, Germany. She has memories of secret staircases in the homes. 

3) In the late 1860s, Victoria spent time with Prussian royal relatives in Berlin and Potsdam. She had her first experiences attending the theater and ballet.
